The '''Algeran Faction''' was a terrorist group based on [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]]. During the rise to power of [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], the Algaran Faction were responsible for several atrocities that were considered to be the worst in Esselian history.

